atory selection criteria for low-metallicity\ncandidates. Selected stars from our validated list are being followed-up with\nhigh-resolution spectroscopy, to reveal their full chemical abundance patterns\nfor further studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 02:59:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
